<p><strong>Calculation Example (Scale-up):</strong> 2,500 tickets/month × 5K tokens per ticket = 12.5M input tokens. Response averaging 10K tokens = 25M output tokens. Claude Opus: (12.5M × $5/M) + (25M × $25/M) = $62.50 + $625 = $687.50 baseline; shown with estimated overhead = $1,187.50/month.</p>

